verbose_text: Polyvinyl chloride (PVC) column experiments were conducted under a rainout shelter during two consecutive seasons (2017-2018 and 2018-2019) at the Crops For the Future-Field Research Center (CFF-FRC) located at 2degrees55'52.2 " N 101degrees52'45.7 " E, altitude 42 m above sea level in Semenyih, Malaysia.
